{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be bold and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EcoThreads - Sustainable Fashion</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #000080; /* Navy Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #ADD8E6; /* Light Blue */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #f4f4f4;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 128, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 128, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/000080/ffffff?text=Sustainable+Fashion'); /* Placeholder image */\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            min-height: 400px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .section h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .products {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n\n        .product-item {\n            width: 30%;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .product-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        .product-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .product-item h4 {\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n        }\n\n        .product-item p {\n            color: #666;\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>EcoThreads</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#products\">Products</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Consciously Crafted. Beautifully Worn.</h2>\n        <p>Discover fashion that cares for the planet and its people.</p>\n        <a href=\"#products\" class=\"cta-button\">Shop Our Collection</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n        <h3>Our Story</h3>\n        <p>At EcoThreads, we believe in a fashion industry that respects the environment. We use only sustainable materials, ethical manufacturing processes, and timeless designs to bring you clothing you can feel good about wearing. Join us in making a difference, one thread at a time.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"products\" class=\"section\" style=\"background-color: var(--secondary-color); color: var(--primary-color);\">\n        <h3>Featured Products</h3>\n        <div class=\"products\">\n            <div class=\"product-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/000080/ffffff?text=Organic+Tee\" alt=\"Organic Cotton T-Shirt\">\n                <h4>Organic Cotton Tee</h4>\n                <p>Soft, breathable, and made from 100% organic cotton.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/000080/ffffff?text=Recycled+Denim\" alt=\"Recycled Denim Jeans\">\n                <h4>Recycled Denim Jeans</h4>\n                <p>Classic fit, crafted from recycled denim materials.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/000080/ffffff?text=Linen+Dress\" alt=\"Linen Sundress\">\n                <h4>Linen Sundress</h4>\n                <p>Lightweight and airy, perfect for warm days.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n        <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n        <p>Have questions or want to collaborate? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n        <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@ecothreads.com\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color); text-decoration: underline;\">info@ecothreads.com</a></p>\n        <p>Follow us on social media!</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 EcoThreads. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll-to-section functionality\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}